items.summary: In WhyChooseUs.tsx, perform a thorough audit of all JSX elements within the '5-Star Rated Service' (or '5-Star Customer Experience') card and remove every arrow, chevron, or directional icon element — including any ArrowRight, ChevronRight, or similar Lucide/SVG icons — that appears anywhere inside that card's heading, label, body, or wrapper. Ensure no arrow or chevron of any kind remains visible on that card after the change.
